==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Awless
<hw>Aw"less</hw> <pr>(⟦add⟧"l⟦ecr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Wanting reverence; void of respectful fear.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Awless</xex> insolence.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Inspiring no awe.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>awless</xex> throne.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>
<altsp> [Written also <asp>aweless</asp>]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Awlessness</ent>⟦br⟧
